quran[5{c,v,t}:
5,109,( woh din yaad rakhnay ke Laiq hai ) jis din khuda payghambaroon ko jama kere ga phir un se pouchye ga ke tumhekiya jawab mila tha woh arz karen ge ke hamein kuch maloom nahi tuhi ghaib ki baton se waaqif hai
5,110,jab khuda ( eesa se ) farmaiye ga ke ae eesa ban maryam! mere un ehsaanon ko yaad karo jo mein ne tum par aur tumhari walida par kiye jab mein ne rooh al quds ( yani jibrael ) se tumhari madad ki tum jhulay mein aur jawan ho kar ( aik hi nasq par ) logon se guftagu karte they aur jab mein ne tum ko kitaab aur danai aur torat aur injeel sikhayi aur jab tum mere hukum se matti ka janwar bana kar is mein phoonk maar dete they to woh mere hukum se urrnay lagta tha aur madar zaad andhay aur safaid daagh walay ko mere hukum se changa kar dete they aur murdy ko mere hukum se ( zindah karkay qabar se ) nikaal khara karte they aur jab mein ne bani Israel ( ke hathon ) ko tum se rok diya jab tum un ke paas khulay nishaan le kar aeye to jo un mein se kafir they kehnay lagey ke yeh Sarih jaadoo hai
5,111,aur jab mein ne hawarion ki taraf hukum bheja ke mujh par aur mere paighambar par imaan lao woh kehnay lagey ke ( perwar-digaar ) hum imaan laaye to Shahid rahev ke hum farmanbardar hain
5,112,( woh qissa bhi yaad karo ) jab hawarion ne kaha ke ae eesa ban maryam!kiya tumhara perwar-digaar aisa kar sakta hai ke hum par aasman se ( ta-aam ka ) khawan nazil kere? unhon ne kaha ke agar imaan rakhtay ho to khuda se daro
5,113,woh bolay ke hamari yeh khwahish hai ke hum is mein se khayen aur hamaray dil tasalii payen aur hum jaan len ke tum ne hum se sach kaha hai aur hum is ( khawan ke nuzool ) par gawah rahen
